description:
Testimonies of Changed Lives - https://www.amazingfacts.org/news-and-features/changed-lives
 Pastor Doug Batchelor's Website - https://www.dougbatchelor.com

The Doug Batchelor story,  as the teenage son of a millionaire father and show-business mother, Doug Batchelor had everything but happiness. Disgusted with himself and convinced that life had no purpose, Doug soon found himself living in a cave.

chapters.title: Leaving a Bible in the cave
